title: DAZ3D - Blind Demon plus Extras
description:
Blind Demon
-----------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/f58241f5e678e6e6dad325eed74da6df.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/34151

From the imagination of film industry creature creator Josh P. Crocket and the studio of Sixus1 comes the "Blind Demon" original figure and product line. Expert CG craftsmanship and cutting edge modern movie artistry come together in a beautifully horrible creation waiting to add it's own brand of macabre to your Daz Studio renders!


Subterranean Texture for Blind Demon
------------------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/e0a086d9113e9ed7cdd644537d4b3a4b.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/34467

Subteranean: a texture/material expansion for "Josh P. Crockett's Blind Demon" from Sixus1.


Rags of The Shunned Outfit for Blind Demon
------------------------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/ff375f41749b7b5417a1257716e3d5c3.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/34489

Rags of the Shunned: a clothing addition for "Josh P. Crockett's Blind Demon" from Sixus1.


Wings of The Fallen
-------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/df787fd6da5448c67b0b3fb20c50ddfc.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/34491

Wings of the Fallen: wings for "Josh P. Crockett's Blind Demon" from Sixus1, with bonus textures/materials complimentary to the Subterranean texture pack, also available here for the Blind Demon original figure.


Sight Regained for Blind Demon
------------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/bb39baa5cb7d67152d941ccb2b6ccfbf.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/34465

Sight Regained: a geo-grafting add on for "Josh P. Crockett's Blind Demon" from Sixus1, replacing the palms of the Blind Demon's hands with articulated eyes, bringing a new level of eerie to your renders!
